Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.82,0:00:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在瞬间明白所有真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.84,0:00:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要开始就不会停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.52,0:00:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是惊人的大翻转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.39,0:00:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登场人数是历代最少的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.44,0:00:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看清事实的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.97,0:00:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似小孩 头脑却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.90,0:00:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就是 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.94,0:01:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在叔叔以前学生时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.63,0:01:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做过家庭教师的惠小姐的父母家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.03,0:01:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了被装置炸弹的车子爆炸了的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.08,0:01:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡的是惠小姐的妹妹宽美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.36,0:01:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为惠小姐不擅长倒车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.54,0:01:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以宽美小姐帮她倒车因而死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.82,0:02:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫌疑犯是个叫做高桥弘昌的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.91,0:02:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和惠小姐的丈夫崎原和夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.24,0:02:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们之间有个交换杀人的交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.48,0:02:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本想杀害惠小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.44,0:02:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来却误杀了宽美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.80,0:02:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来那两个人已经认罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.73,0:02:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也以为事件就这样解决了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.69,0:02:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么狭窄的空间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.08,0:02:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然能轻易的倒车出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.69,0:02:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个事件 还没有结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.20,0:02:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汽车爆炸事件的真相（后篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.38,0:02:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 你怎么突然跑开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.75,0:02:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.91,0:02:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.91,0:02:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠小姐为了我们特地买了蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.75,0:02:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们赶快去她家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.38,0:02:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 他到底在想些什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.88,0:03:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在告诉叔叔还嫌太早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.72,0:03:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多掌握一些证据才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.46,0:03:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这次的意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.39,0:03:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 该怎么讲好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.14,0:03:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 我已经没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.13,0:03:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要再替我担心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.31,0:03:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个红茶 趁热喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.62,0:03:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.72,0:03:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.89,0:03:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南也过来吃蛋糕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.80,0:03:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问洗手间在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.89,0:03:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是那间吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.71,0:04:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崎原在二楼的书房里特别装了一个专用电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.18,0:04:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都是用那部电话联系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.70,0:04:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.86,0:04:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是撕掉胶布后的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.55,0:04:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.18,0:04:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然那里装有那个东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.14,0:05:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠小姐比想象中还要有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.06,0:05:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也放心了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.39,0:05:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看她那样子应该没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.73,0:05:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了米花车站之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.26,0:05:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有别的事要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.92,0:05:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们先回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.35,0:05:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也没什么啦 不过可别太晚回来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.51,0:05:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.83,0:05:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里竟然有个窗户
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.37,0:05:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 如果从这个窗户的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.11,0:05:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.55,0:05:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 这样我就了解整个情况了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就剩下证据了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.67,0:06:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.79,0:06:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.33,0:06:14.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于这次的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.48,0:06:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有几个地方觉得很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.04,0:06:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.23,0:06:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天惠小姐不是从超市那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.13,0:06:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狭窄的停车位倒车出来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.19,0:06:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而案发当时为什么要她妹妹帮她倒车出来呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.83,0:06:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有惠小姐家二楼书房里面的电话线附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.87,0:06:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有胶布被撕掉的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.10,0:06:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里到底贴过什么东西呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.51,0:06:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胶布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.65,0:06:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 案发的那栋房子里面有一扇秘窗你知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.92,0:06:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为爆炸所以玻璃破掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.46,0:06:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然从里面钉上了木板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.60,0:07:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过从那里就可以看到车了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.16,0:07:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不错的设计
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.83,0:07:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想说些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.21,0:07:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说小惠和这个事件有关吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.32,0:07:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.51,0:07:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.64,0:07:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.73,0:07:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最了解她的为人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.04,0:07:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她是我的学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.32,0:07:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔认识的是高中时代的惠小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.69,0:07:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进入社会后 惠小姐也许改变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.19,0:07:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.29,0:07:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.76,0:07:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前完全一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔心里很想这么认为的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.11,0:07:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.09,0:07:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 事实上她已经…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.50,0:07:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦 上楼去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.81,0:07:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去冲凉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.43,0:08:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这臭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.94,0:08:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然讲这种话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.77,0:08:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密的窗户
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.71,0:08:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 是我和宽美之间这样称呼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.57,0:08:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸以前常常在这里看我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.13,0:08:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这里已经很久没用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.38,0:08:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过小的时候我们在门前捣蛋时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常常在这里被看到而被骂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.13,0:08:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想问崎原和高桥的犯罪证物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.73,0:08:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我想看一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.10,0:08:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后还有什么新发现吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.54,0:08:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于死者宽美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.71,0:08:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听她的朋友说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.94,0:09:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在年轻的时候曾经抢过两次惠小姐的恋人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.91,0:09:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是自由恋爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.33,0:09:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说宽美小姐是为了好玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.62,0:09:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算很文静的惠小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.59,0:09:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在与崎原结婚的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.73,0:09:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也半开玩笑的告诉宽美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.47,0:09:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这次再犯 别怪我不客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.99,0:09:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想叔叔应该可以找到几个推断的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.57,0:09:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是最主要的证据…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.37,0:09:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 说不定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.94,0:09:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警官 刚才在电话中拜托你的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.22,0:10:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我叫高木确认过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.09,0:10:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙只有在那次超市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.36,0:10:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到惠小姐一次而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.19,0:10:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后他就没在惠小姐面前出现过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.13,0:10:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时高桥的装扮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.69,0:10:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴着帽子还有墨镜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.40,0:10:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.57,0:10:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利 一大早你到底怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.18,0:10:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 警官 再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.16,0:10:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.04,0:10:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 终于找到证据了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.48,0:11:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.13,0:11:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.83,0:11:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 小兰姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.75,0:11:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸从秋叶原打电话来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.59,0:11:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说现在要到惠小姐家去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.00,0:11:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说只有他才能说服的了她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.59,0:11:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸到底在讲些什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.75,0:11:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰姐姐 我们也去惠小姐家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.49,0:11:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 为什么连你们也来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.99,0:11:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.35,0:11:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有点关心爸爸电话里讲的那件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.93,0:11:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.02,0:11:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.68,0:12:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 老师 你说有事要告诉我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.84,0:12:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠 今天我来是劝你自首的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.41,0:12:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.57,0:12:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.60,0:12:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于你丈夫和你妹妹交往的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.37,0:12:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有他和高桥交换杀人的约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.68,0:12:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.86,0:12:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果你就利用这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.96,0:12:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将多年憎恨的妹妹给除掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.56,0:12:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把这个杀人罪嫁祸给你先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.30,0:12:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 你怎么突然这样讲呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.76,0:12:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先你在两个月前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.09,0:12:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在秋叶原那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.00,0:12:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买了窃听器和自动录音机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.16,0:12:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还向店员详细的询问使用方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.36,0:12:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是和你买的同样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.09,0:13:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窃听器和自动录音机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.31,0:13:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.45,0:13:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才向你借洗手间的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.57,0:13:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去调查过二楼的书房了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.74,0:13:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你将这窃听器装在你丈夫的书房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.10,0:13:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷听他和高桥之间的谈话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.60,0:13:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墙壁旁边留下的胶布痕迹就是证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.55,0:13:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一开始你是想偷听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.00,0:13:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丈夫和你妹妹之间的谈话吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.07,0:13:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是后来你发现了这个秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.92,0:13:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你丈夫和不认识的男人做了交换杀人的约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.23,0:13:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他也已经杀死了对方的妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.26,0:13:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.50,0:13:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮到你被高桥杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.13,0:13:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为高桥会在车子上装置炸弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.98,0:13:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是装在这个家的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.60,0:13:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道你丈夫也会被怀疑因而困惑着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.02,0:14:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后你就告诉你丈夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.07,0:14:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要开车回父母家去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.13,0:14:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好你妹妹的车子送去保养
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.37,0:14:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以车库是空出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.99,0:14:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丈夫听到这些话之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.82,0:14:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用外面的公共电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.14,0:14:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉高桥这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.39,0:14:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你不知道那个电话的内容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.80,0:14:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过大概知道高桥不会错过这次机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.36,0:14:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而回娘家去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.61,0:14:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在回家的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.72,0:14:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你不擅长倒车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.63,0:14:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你妹妹帮你把车子开出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.69,0:14:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后和计划的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.67,0:14:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹就这样死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.65,0:14:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是这个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.10,0:14:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了意料之外的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.18,0:14:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我突然去找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.85,0:14:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惊慌的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.32,0:14:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下 老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.75,0:14:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.83,0:14:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来 过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.39,0:15:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果现在不做的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.51,0:15:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怕会被做侦探的我给揭穿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.29,0:15:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的确买了窃听器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.20,0:15:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怕丈夫有外遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.68,0:15:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在桌子底下装了窃听器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.04,0:15:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过很快我就后悔 然后丢掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.13,0:15:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我根本没用过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.90,0:15:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道外遇的对象是你妹妹吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.84,0:15:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.43,0:15:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如 我是说假如
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.43,0:15:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和老师推理的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.72,0:15:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会被判什么罪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.51,0:15:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在车子装置炸弹的是那个叫做高桥的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.75,0:16:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教唆他这么做的人是我丈夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.28,0:16:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我所做的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.25,0:16:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许被装置炸弹的车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.00,0:16:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让妹妹去开而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.24,0:16:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是杀人的共犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.60,0:16:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是恐吓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.83,0:16:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗 老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.32,0:16:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是法律部的学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.73,0:16:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律师的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.32,0:16:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确如你所讲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.23,0:16:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是让你妹妹去开车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.56,0:16:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一点罪也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.53,0:16:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.18,0:16:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.09,0:16:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你让机率很高肯定装有炸弹的车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.55,0:16:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你妹妹去开的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.36,0:16:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会变成杀人罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.25,0:16:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那天随便找个借口跑到储藏室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.59,0:16:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从窗户那里偷看着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.24,0:17:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果和你预料的一样 高桥走了进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.50,0:17:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将炸弹装在车子上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.64,0:17:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当你确认过后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.75,0:17:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就拜托你妹妹帮你把车开出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.60,0:17:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.61,0:17:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在非常高的机率之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.73,0:17:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你妹妹去开装有炸弹的车子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.99,0:17:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有证据说我曾经多次去看过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.73,0:17:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,储藏室那个窗户吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.65,0:17:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有的话 请现在马上拿出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.76,0:17:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在马上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.26,0:17:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证据的话 就在叔叔的身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.86,0:17:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是上次惠小姐在医院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.88,0:17:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画的高桥先生的画像啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.49,0:17:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠小姐说在哪里见过他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.27,0:17:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就…就是在家附近的超市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.78,0:17:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.05,0:17:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为警官先生讲过那个叫做高桥的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.02,0:17:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在超市跟踪时是戴着墨镜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.26,0:18:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那张画像上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.05,0:18:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有戴着墨镜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.85,0:18:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.03,0:18:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实惠小姐在超市那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.47,0:18:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没发觉被一个叫做高桥的人跟踪过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.88,0:18:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你之后偷听他打电话给崎原时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.84,0:18:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才知道有这个人的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.09,0:18:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么那个脸是在哪里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.20,0:18:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.60,0:18:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是在那秘密的窗户看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.99,0:18:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠 你在父母家这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.71,0:18:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那储藏室的窗户偷看着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.14,0:18:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在下面装置炸弹的高桥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.00,0:19:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.71,0:19:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天 不想让人看到他的高桥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.56,0:19:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在进入车库前还戴着墨镜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.95,0:19:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 离开车库的时候也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.84,0:19:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 只有一次必须摘下墨镜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.61,0:19:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在装置炸弹的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.50,0:19:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为装置炸弹这种危险的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.52,0:19:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有人戴着墨镜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.60,0:19:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在漆黑的车库里面动手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.14,0:19:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 这张没有戴墨镜的画像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.67,0:19:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你在储藏室偷看高桥的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.47,0:20:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师说的对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.08,0:20:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的确偷听到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.48,0:20:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.41,0:20:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想杀了我然后将保险金和父母留给我的遗产
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.49,0:20:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部拿出来给宽美做开店的资金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.83,0:20:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候真的很快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.46,0:20:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.47,0:20:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是最幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.70,0:20:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.42,0:20:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直希望回到那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.48,0:20:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.16,0:20:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15年前我应该教导你一个最重要的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.21,0:20:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比读书还重要的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.68,0:21:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样的我也和妻子分居了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.52,0:21:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也没资格讲你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.37,0:21:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.45,0:21:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在还来得及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.67,0:21:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着罪再次重新学习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.44,0:21:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是学习如何做人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.72,0:21:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时候 你还愿意教我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.62,0:21:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.03,0:23:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件解决是件好事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.24,0:23:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过叔叔这次好像伤得很重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.35,0:23:18.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.17,0:23:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是毛利侦探事务所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.18,0:23:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 洋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.50,0:23:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.52,0:23:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 演唱会吗 我当然会去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.85,0:23:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了洋子 啦啦队家庭教师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.87,0:23:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都愿意做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.84,0:23:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来根本不用我们担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.51,0:23:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 真是个超快恢复精神的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.32,0:23:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 小兰姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.61,0:23:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是觉得那个戴眼镜的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.90,0:23:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在哪里见过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.42,0:24:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.79,0:24:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里见过他 小兰姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.66,0:24:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.17,0:24:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.76,0:24:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园子的夏日海滩冒险物语（前篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.72,0:24:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.95,0:24:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园子的照相机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.69,0:24:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.42,0:24:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 兰 那件泳衣真大胆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.19,0:24:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,园子你才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.46,0:00:21.41,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开所有杂志还是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.76,0:00:25.38,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在这摇头叹息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.64,0:00:29.74,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有适合我的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.89,0:00:33.80,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世纪末的流行色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.11,0:00:37.85,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都无法讨得你的欢心 惹得你满腔怒火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.03,0:00:41.64,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很抱歉如临深渊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.78,0:00:46.48,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像走在悬崖边缘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.95,0:00:50.61,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇摇欲坠的感觉有什么不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.73,0:00:54.60,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样也一定要向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.00,0:00:59.27,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子汉 一点也不是问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.22,0:01:08.32,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不到紧要关头不出手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.43,0:01:12.12,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 不要用冷淡的眼光看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.31,0:01:15.94,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我用自己的速度前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.31,0:01:20.17,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则我马上会崩溃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.65,0:01:24.17,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像走在悬崖边缘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.66,0:01:28.14,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇摇欲坠的感觉有什么不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.58,0:01:32.68,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样也一定要向前走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.00,0:01:37.31,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子汉 一点也不是问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.55,0:21:47.19,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这孕育着神秘的夜里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.72,0:21:51.86,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请闭上眼睛 献上你的祈祷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.64,0:21:58.20,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这月光融融的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.77,0:22:04.62,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈说我们因为爱而生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.12,0:22:15.89,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 一切都停滞不前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.50,0:22:22.18,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼看未来化为碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.46,0:22:30.89,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 赤着脚 踩在大地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.01,0:22:36.32,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨越彩虹 抓住天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.10,0:22:42.84,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我祈祷 抓住胸前的十字架 在白天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.98,0:22:49.16,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望照耀着你 在夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.28,0:22:55.34,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温暖的光芒 将你拥抱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.49,0:23:02.08,Ending,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远为你停留 为你的爱而停留
